reviews.review_text:
No reviews-LET ME BE THE FIRST! Just imagine if this was your 1st show and your friends talked you into seeing the Grateful Dead.
And then these guys hop on stage and really do sound like the Dreadful Grapes.
Wow, I can't even imagine trying to trip my way thru this.
I could freak out if I detected a stray note or a blown vocal.during a hot show.  
If I played this for my old lady I could go sleep in the shed forget the couch.
